plot: Nombre Original: The Phantom of the Opera at the Royal Albert Hall (London, UK)Director: Cameron MackintoshActores: Ramin Karimloo as 'The Phantom' and Sierra Boggess as 'Christine'.A disfigured musical genius, hidden away in the Paris Opera House, terrorizes the opera company for the unwitting benefit of a young protégée whom he trains and loves.
